{
  "stem": "24195.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I got just cabin fever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I couldn't be any longer in that house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I had to get out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I'm driving through the deserted streets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The Russians are not here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The Russians are just in the process of approaching the city and circling the city.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm driving through.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for some reason, I'm driving past the chancellery, where Hitler is.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Honestly, I don't know how I got out there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- suddenly, I see SS soldiers loading up files and all kinds of other things on-- on trucks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were getting ready to evacuate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some of them got out, because there was still one highway open to the west, that the Russians hadn't cut off yet.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but I was crazy doing that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they could have-- but they were too busy [LAUGHS] worrying about their own fate, you know, than asking any more questions.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I got back, hid in the cellar with the other rest of the people, and the Battle of Berlin started.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was thundering.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had these rocket launchers that have eight or 15 you know, guns on one-- on one-- on one mobile platform-- mobilized platform.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And those things, when they go off, they make a hellish noise.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, it's just-- deafening.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it's just-- I was-- and those poor guys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One day, I went out to get some bread, because the people-- somebody said there is a bakery still open in the vicinity.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and we were out of bread, and people were starving in that basement.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was the only one that was young.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the only other men were real old ones left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they asked me, would I dare?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I went out and get-- to go to that store, but it was bad.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
